content.rendered:
Crystal Clear Case Designed for Apple iPhone XR with Reinforced Bumpers. Upgraded Anti-Yellow Transparent Material Makes the iPhone XR Case Show Off The Original Beauty of Your Phone. Newest Dustproof Speaker Can Prevent Dust from Entering Your Phone and Will Help With Keeping your Phone Protected at All Times for Longer Use. Full Coverage Protection Case Prevents the Screen and Camera From Rubbing and Scratching From Accidental Mishaps. Precise Cutouts & Responsive Buttons Ensures Easy Access to All Commands and Functions. Ergonomic Texture Offers Comfortable Grip, Anti-Fingerprint, Anti-Scratch, and Anti-Slip.

Make positive this suits by getting into your mannequin quantity.
[360° Full Protection] – This iPhone XR Protective Phone Case Offers Full Coverage Protection to The Camera Lens, Back and Bumpers of the Mobile. With Enhanced Raised Lips of two.0mm Closely Wraps the Screen Which Protects from Potential Damage. Double Protection Prevents the Display and Camera from Rubbing and Scratching on Rough Flat Surfaces.
[Anti-Yellow Material] – Made With Anti-Yellow Material and Advanced Micro Dot Technology, which Prevents Discoloring which Ensures a Pristine Finish. This iPhone XR Clear Case Enhances the Stylistic Appearance with its Transparent Finish however Also Provides the Protection Needed to Tackle Everyday Mishaps.
[Reinforced Shock Absorber] – With Four Shock-Absorbing Airbags, the iPhone XR Shockproof Case Provides Prefect Protection Against Accidental Falls and Dropping. The Soft Silicone Case is Scratch-Resistant, Anti-Slip Resistant and Very Durable.
[Easy to Use] – Perfect Cut Outs for Speakers, Camera and All Ports for the iPhone XR. Soft TPU bumper permits you simple to placed on and take off. Also Screen Protector Compatible.
